30 January 1999
Manda called me after she finished working out at the gym on her side of town at like 8:33pm today. &ldquo;Do you think there&rsquo;s any way I can get to the museum by 9 o&rsquo;clock? They&rsquo;re playing Beastie Boys laser light show.&rdquo;
Oooh. I didn&rsquo;t really think so, but we love the B-Boys. &ldquo;Um, try it and I&rsquo;ll meet you at the ticket counter.&rdquo;
Actually, at my request Manda called me back some minutes later when she reached Fondren on Hwy 59.
